msgid "11500:もし――[linebreak]これをあやせに黙って持っていったら、この剣は僕のものになるんだろうか。[%p]"
msgstr "11500:Maybe... Maybe if I just took it without telling Ayase... it would be mine then, right?[%p]"

msgid "11600:労せずしてディソードを手に入れられるなら、なりふり構っている場合じゃない。[linebreak]僕の中で欲望がせり上がってくる。[%p]"
msgstr "11600:If I could get a Di-Sword that easily, then all my problems would be solved, right?[%p]"

msgid "11700:ゴクリと息を呑み、恐る恐る、剣へと手を伸ばした。[linebreak]柄の部分を、つかむ。[%p]"
msgstr "11700:I gulped and reached out for the weapon with a trembling hand. I went to grab the blade.[%p]"

msgid "11800:つかんだ、つもりだった。[%p]"
msgstr "11800:I thought I'd grabbed it, but...[%p]"

msgid "11900:でも手は、剣をすり抜けていた。握りしめたのは空気だけ。もう一度試してみるけど、結果は同じだった。[%p]"
msgstr "11900:My hand passed right through it. I'd grabbed only thin air. I tried again, but the same thing happened.[%p]"

msgid "12000:つかめない。触れることさえできない。[%p]"
msgstr "12000:I couldn't take it. I couldn't even touch it.[%p]"

msgid "12100:今、この剣はリアルブートされていない、っていうことなんだろうか。[linebreak]周囲共通認識が為されていないから、ただのあやせの妄想でしかない状態。[%p]"
msgstr "12100:Was the sword not real booted right now? And since there was no shared awareness of its existence, it was just a delusion of Ayase's?[%p]"

msgid "12200:幻。[linebreak]夢。[linebreak]残像。[%p]"
msgstr "12200:An illusion... A dream... An afterimage.[%p]"

msgid "12300:[name]三住[line]「なにやってんだ、お前？」[%p]"
msgstr "12300:[name]三住[line]What the hell are you doing?[%p]"

msgid "12400:僕を見て、三住くんが不思議そうな顔をしていた。[%p]"
msgstr "12400:Misumi was looking at me, confused.[%p]"

msgid "12500:それから１０分ほど待っても、あやせが戻ってくる気配はなかった。[linebreak]トイレに行ったはずの梨深も来ない。どこに行ったんだろう。[%p]"
msgstr "12500:We waited another ten minutes, but there was no sign of Ayase. Rimi, who'd supposedly just gone to the bathroom, was nowhere to be seen, either. Where had she gone?[%p]"

msgid "12600:[name]三住[line]「梨深ってこの病室の場所、知ってたか？」[%p]"
msgstr "12600:[name]三住[line]Did Rimi know what room Ayase was in?[%p]"

msgid "12700:[name]拓巳[line]「あ……」[%p]"
msgstr "12700:[name]拓巳[line]Ah...[%p]"

msgid "12800:病室の場所をナースステーションで聞いたのは、梨深と別れた後だ。もしかして場所が分からなくてどこかをさまよっているのかも。[%p]"
msgstr "12800:We'd asked about the room at the nurse's station after splitting up with Rimi. She might be wandering around, looking for us.[%p]"

msgid "12900:[name]三住[line]「あいつバカだからな。[linebreak]俺たちみたいに、誰かに聞こうって発想がないのかもしんねえぞ」[%p]"
msgstr "12900:[name]三住[line]Rimi's pretty dumb. She might not think of asking somebody like we did.[%p]"

msgid "13000:[name]拓巳[line]「……さ、探しに……」[%p]"
msgstr "13000:[name]拓巳[line]L-Let's go look for her.[%p]"

msgid "13100:梨深が一緒じゃないと、不安だ。[linebreak]この病院だって、安全とは言い切れない。[%p]"
msgstr "13100:I was nervous without her around. There was no way to know for sure if this hospital was safe.[%p]"

msgid "13200:『将軍』が僕を思考盗撮しているなら、[linebreak]ここにいることだって知られているはず。[%p]"
msgstr "13200:If Shogun was reading my mind, he'd know exactly where I was.[%p]"

msgid "13300:[name]三住[line]「そうだな。待つのも飽きたし、[linebreak]タクもあいつがいないと寂しいだろうからな。ははっ」[%p]"
msgstr "13300:[name]三住[line]Yeah. I'm tired of waiting. And you're probably pretty lonely without her. Haha.[%p]"

msgid "13400:[name]拓巳[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "13400:[name]拓巳[line]...[%p]"

msgid "13500:[name]三住[line]「なあ、ぶっちゃけ、梨深とはどうなんだ？」[%p]"
msgstr "13500:[name]三住[line]Hey, tell me the truth. What's the deal with you and Rimi?[%p]"

msgid "13600:[name]拓巳[line]「え？」[%p]"
msgstr "13600:[name]拓巳[line]Huh?[%p]"

msgid "13700:[name]三住[line]「付き合ってんのかって聞いてんだよ。[linebreak]お前ら、最近けっこういい感じじゃね？」[%p]"
msgstr "13700:[name]三住[line]I'm asking if she's your girlfriend. You two are spending an awful lot of time together, right?[%p]"

msgid "13800:[name]拓巳[line]「……つ、付き合って、ないよ」[%p]"
msgstr "13800:[name]拓巳[line]W-We're not... dating.[%p]"

msgid "13900:言いながらも、顔が火照ってしまう。[%p]"
msgstr "13900:As I spoke, my face flushed.[%p]"

msgid "14000:僕と、梨深が、付き合う……か。[%p]"
msgstr "14000:Me and Rimi... dating.[%p]"

msgid "14100:確かに何度か妄想したことはある。[%p]"
msgstr "14100:I'd had some delusions about the idea, sure.[%p]"

msgid "14200:三次元に興味はなかったけど、いまや僕の中で梨深の存在はかなり大きなものになりつつある。[%p]"
msgstr "14200:I wasn't into 3D girls, but Rimi was a pretty big part of my life now.[%p]"

msgid "14300:でも前に梨深が“一緒にいてあげる”って言ってくれたとき、[linebreak]同時にこうも言ってた。[%p]"
msgstr "14300:But when Rimi had offered to stay by my side, she'd also said this.[%p]"

msgid "14400:[name]梨深[line]「そんなの、友達だからに決まってるでしょ」[%p]"
msgstr "14400:[name]梨深[line]Because we're friends, right?[%p]"

msgid "14500:つまり友達としか見られていないっていうこと。[%p]"
msgstr "14500:In other words, she saw me as a friend.[%p]"

msgid "14600:僕みたいなキモオタと恋人の関係になろうなんて、きっと向こうはまったく考えてないだろう。[%p]"
msgstr "14600:She'd have no interest in dating a creepy otaku like me, obviously.[%p]"

msgid "14700:そもそも梨深って、そういうのに鈍感そうだし。[%p]"
msgstr "14700:And Rimi didn't seem like the type who'd want to date, anyway.[%p]"

msgid "14800:僕は三住くんと手分けして、梨深かあやせを探すことにした。[%p]"
msgstr "14800:Misumi and I decided to split up and look for her.[%p]"

msgid "14900:三住くんが階段を下っていったので、僕は上の階を探してみることにした。[%p]"
msgstr "14900:Misumi checked the floor below, so I went to check the one above us.[%p]"

msgid "15000:[name]男[line]「あみぃちゃん！\u3000ろこぉ！？\u3000あみぃちゃん！」[%p]"
msgstr "15000:[name]男[line]Ami! Where are you? Ami![%p]"

msgid "15100:５０代くらいの初老の入院患者と、廊下ですれ違った。男はよたよたと歩きながら、しきりに“あみぃちゃん”なる人の名を呼んでいる。[%p]"
msgstr "15100:I passed by an elderly man in his 50s. He was clearly a patient here. He was slowly staggering down the hallway, calling out for “Ami,” whoever that was.[%p]"

msgid "15200:僕はそれを無視して廊下の奥へ。[%p]"
msgstr "15200:I ignored him and kept walking.[%p]"

msgid "15300:病院内を歩き回ることにはそれほど抵抗はない。[linebreak]昔からよく通っていたからだろう。[%p]"
msgstr "15300:Walking around the hospital didn't really bother me as much as I'd thought it would. It was probably because I'd been here so many times.[%p]"

msgid "15400:ただ、廊下の角や扉が開いたままの病室から『将軍』が現れないかとドキドキしてしまう。[%p]"
msgstr "15400:Still, the thought that Shogun might appear from behind every corner or open door made my heart race.[%p]"

msgid "15500:それに、どこからかたまに聞こえてくる悲鳴のような奇声も心臓に悪い。[%p]"
msgstr "15500:There were those strange screams I sometimes heard, too. They were bad for my heart.[%p]"

msgid "15600:廊下は全体的にクリーム色で統一されていた。[%p]"
msgstr "15600:The walls and floor of the hallway were all the same off-white color.[%p]"

msgid "15700:扉が開いている病室とそうでない病室がある。『将軍』の気配がないか確かめようと、いくつかの病室の中をのぞいてみた。[%p]"
msgstr "15700:Some doors were open, and some weren't. I peeked inside a few of them to see if Shogun was lurking there.[%p]"

msgid "15800:どの病室もベッドがふたつ並んでいて、シーツが人の形にふくらんでいた。そこに患者が寝ているんだろう。ただ、顔は死角になっていて見えなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "15800:Each room had two beds, and I could see human-shaped forms beneath the sheets. Those must have been patients, sleeping. But for some reason, all of them were turned away from me, and I couldn't see their faces.[%p]"

msgid "15900:廊下を歩いている人の姿はあまりない。[%p]"
msgstr "15900:There weren't many people out in the hallway.[%p]"

msgid "16000:さっきの“あみぃちゃん”を呼んでいたおっさんと、看護師がひとり。今のところすれ違ったのはその２人だけ。[%p]"
msgstr "16000:There'd been the old man calling for “Ami,” and then a nurse. They'd been the only two I'd seen.[%p]"

msgid "16100:あまりここにはいたくない。[linebreak]なぜかそんな気がした。[%p]"
msgstr "16100:I didn't want to stay here for too much longer. I wasn't sure why, but that's how it felt.[%p]"

msgid "16200:雰囲気が重苦しい。不快感はないけど、僕はここにいちゃいけないような気がする。[%p]"
msgstr "16200:The air felt heavy. It wasn't unpleasant, but it felt like I didn't belong here.[%p]"

msgid "16300:なおも先に進むと右側へと折れるような形で曲がり角になっていた。[%p]"
msgstr "16300:As I kept going forward, I saw that the hallway turned to the right.[%p]"

msgid "16400:その先に病室がさらに続いているんだろうか。そう思いながら、恐る恐る曲がってみると――[%p]"
msgstr "16400:There must be more rooms down there, I thought. As I nervously rounded the corner...[%p]"

msgid "16500:いきなり、目の前が壁だった。[%p]"
msgstr "16500:I saw a wall right in front of me.[%p]"

msgid "16600:しかも、それまでのクリーム色がウソのように、曲がった先の突き当たりだけが黒いペンキで塗り潰されている。[%p]"
msgstr "16600:Unlike the off-white of the other walls, this one was painted pure black.[%p]"

msgid "16700:[name]拓巳[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "16700:[name]拓巳[line]...[%p]"

msgid "16800:なぜか――[linebreak]動悸が速まる。[%p]"
msgstr "16800:For some reason... My heart began to race faster and faster.[%p]"

msgid "16900:その場から一歩も動けなくなる。[%p]"
msgstr "16900:I couldn't move.[%p]"

msgid "17000:視界がグラグラと揺れる。[%p]"
msgstr "17000:My vision began to swim.[%p]"

msgid "17100:激しい目眩かと思って目を閉じ、まぶたの上から指で揉んでみると、自分の目玉が痙攣していた。[%p]"
msgstr "17100:I thought I was just feeling dizzy and closed my eyes. But when I put my fingers on my eyelids, I could feel my eyes twitching beneath them.[%p]"

msgid "17200:足許から這い上がってくる、氷のように冷たい悪寒。[%p]"
msgstr "17200:A cold feeling, like ice, worked its way up my body from below.[%p]"

msgid "17300:呼吸すら忘れ、僕は立ち尽くす。[%p]"
msgstr "17300:I stood there, completely still, forgetting to breathe.[%p]"

msgid "17400:目の前の黒を、見つめる。[%p]"
msgstr "17400:I stared at the black in front of me.[%p]"

msgid "17500:吸い込まれそうな。[linebreak]呑み込まれそうな。[%p]"
msgstr "17500:It felt like it was pulling me, drawing me in.[%p]"

msgid "17600:どこまでも深い黒。[%p]"
msgstr "17600:An endless black that continued on for eternity...[%p]"

msgid "17700:なにもないはずなのに。[linebreak]どこからか見られている。[%p]"
msgstr "17700:There was nothing there, but somebody was watching me.[%p]"

msgid "17800:“神の視線”が僕のうなじに突き刺さってくる。[linebreak]その存在感は、ベースにいるときの比じゃなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "17800:I could feel the Gaze of God stabbing into the back of my neck. It was far, far worse than it had ever been at the Base.[%p]"

msgid "17900:見るな――[%p]"
msgstr "17900:Don't look at me—[%p]"

msgid "18000:[name]拓巳[line]「……っ」[%p]"
msgstr "18000:[name]拓巳[line]...[%p]"

msgid "18100:すべての精神力を使って、まぶたを閉じた。[%p]"
msgstr "18100:I used every scrap of mental power I had to force my eyes closed.[%p]"

msgid "18200:その瞬間に、呼吸ができるようになり、僕はゼイゼイと息をしながら後ずさる。[%p]"
msgstr "18200:Only then could I breathe. Panting, I stepped back.[%p]"

msgid "18300:そのまま顔を伏せ、逃げるように廊下を引き返した。[%p]"
msgstr "18300:I lowered my head, turned around, and ran.[%p]"

msgid "18400:あやせの病室がある階へと早足で戻り、ゼイゼイと息をつく。[%p]"
msgstr "18400:I headed back to the floor Ayase's room was on as fast as I could, stopping to catch my breath only after I'd headed down the stairs.[%p]"

msgid "18500:うなじに触れてみると、粘つくような汗がにじみ出ていた。うなじだけじゃない、全身が汗でねとついている。[%p]"
msgstr "18500:I touched my neck and found it was covered with a thick, sticky layer of sweat. It wasn't just my neck. My whole body was soaked.[%p]"

msgid "18600:いったい、なんだったんだろう……。[linebreak]『将軍』に思考盗撮されているのか？[%p]"
msgstr "18600:What the hell was that? Was it Shogun reading my mind?[%p]"

msgid "18700:“神の視線”の気配は消えてくれない。[%p]"
msgstr "18700:I could still sense the Gaze of God.[%p]"

msgid "18800:息苦しさや悪寒も治まらない。[%p]"
msgstr "18800:It was still hard to breathe. I was still cold.[%p]"

msgid "18900:気持ちが一気に萎えた。[%p]"
msgstr "18900:I felt exhausted.[%p]"

msgid "19000:もう帰りたい。[%p]"
msgstr "19000:I wanted to go home.[%p]"

msgid "19100:梨深に付き添ってもらって、ベースに引きこもってしまいたい。[%p]"
msgstr "19100:I wanted to have Rimi take me back to the Base, and then I could stay there and never leave it again.[%p]"

msgid "19200:そもそも僕なんかが見舞いに来たところで、あやせは喜ぶどころかウザがるだろう。[%p]"
msgstr "19200:Even if I did manage to find Ayase, she'd be annoyed, not happy, to see me.[%p]"

msgid "19300:三住くんの下心丸出しのこの見舞いに、僕が付き合うのもバカげてる。[%p]"
msgstr "19300:Misumi was only here because he was trying to get laid. I was an idiot to play along with it.[%p]"

msgid "19400:帰ろう――[%p]"
msgstr "19400:I should just go home,[%p]"

msgid "19500:『将軍』や優愛が現れる前に。[%p]"
msgstr "19500:before Shogun and Yua show up.[%p]"

msgid "19600:あいつらは神出鬼没だ。[%p]"
msgstr "19600:Those two could appear anywhere, at any time.[%p]"

msgid "19700:僕の居場所を簡単に突き止めてくる。[%p]"
msgstr "19700:They'd be able to find me easily.[%p]"

msgid "19800:どこにいたって気を引き締めていないとダメだ。[%p]"
msgstr "19800:I couldn't relax, anywhere.[%p]"

msgid "19900:僕はよろよろと、壁に手を添えながらあやせの病室を目指した。三住くんは戻ってきているだろうか。梨深と合流できたことを願って、のろのろと歩を進める。[%p]"
msgstr "19900:I headed back to Ayase's room. I was staggering, barely able to walk. I had to put my hand on the wall for support. Was Misumi back, I wondered? I slowly kept moving forward, praying that he'd managed to find Rimi.[%p]"

msgid "20000:[name]看護師Ａ[line]「――山井さんが、またあみぃちゃんっていう名前を呼んでたんですよ」[%p]"
msgstr "20000:[name]看護師Ａ[line]Mr. Yamai was calling out for “Ami” again.[%p]"

msgid "20100:看護師の話し声が、前方から聞こえてくる。[linebreak]顔を上げると、２人のナースがこっちに歩いてくるところだった。[linebreak]ひとりはまだ若く、もうひとりは恰幅のいいおばさん。[%p]"
msgstr "20100:I could hear the voices of the nurses in front of me. I looked up to see two nurses walking towards me. One was young, the other was a plump older woman.[%p]"

msgid "20200:[name]看護師Ａ[line]「いったい誰のことを探してるのか……」[%p]"
msgstr "20200:[name]看護師Ａ[line]Who's he looking for, do you think?[%p]"

msgid "20300:[name]看護師長[line]「それ、この病院に伝わる怪談よ」[%p]"
msgstr "20300:[name]看護師長[line]It's an old ghost story about this hospital.[%p]"

msgid "20400:[name]看護師長[line]「誰も知らない幻の病室があって、そこに“あみぃちゃん”が入院してるらしいわ」[%p]"
msgstr "20400:[name]看護師長[line]There's a room here that nobody can find. And it belongs to a patient named “Ami.”[%p]"

msgid "20500:[name]看護師長[line]「もう何年も前からある噂」[%p]"
msgstr "20500:[name]看護師長[line]The rumor's been around for years.[%p]"

msgid "20600:僕は、顔を伏せてその２人が通り過ぎるのを待つ。息を止めて、荒い呼吸をごまかす。[%p]"
msgstr "20600:I put my head down and waited for the two of them to pass. I held my breath so that they couldn't hear how much trouble I was having breathing.[%p]"

msgid "20700:明らかに不審そうな目で見られていると分かったけど、とにかく無視するしかなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "20700:I could tell they were looking at me suspiciously, but all I could do was try to ignore them.[%p]"

msgid "20800:看護師２人をやり過ごし、なおも必死に歩いていくと、ナースステーションに辿り着いた。[%p]"
msgstr "20800:When they were gone, I started to walk again. Somehow, I managed to make it to the nurse's station.[%p]"

msgid "20900:あやせの病室はもっと手前だったはずで、どうやら行きすぎてしまったらしい。[%p]"
msgstr "20900:Ayase's room was in front of the nurse's station. I must've passed it.[%p]"

msgid "21000:僕は舌打ちし、額の汗を拭う。[linebreak]まだ、見られている気配がする。[%p]"
msgstr "21000:I groaned and wiped the sweat off my forehead. It still felt like somebody was watching me.[%p]"

msgid "21100:ズキズキと胸の奥が痛む。[linebreak]耳鳴りもしている。[%p]"
msgstr "21100:I could feel a piercing sensation in my chest. My ears were ringing, too.[%p]"

msgid "21200:すごく気持ちが悪い。[linebreak]体調は最悪だ。[%p]"
msgstr "21200:I felt awful. It seemed like I might pass out at any moment.[%p]"

msgid "21300:来るときはこんなことなかったのに。[linebreak]僕の身体はいったいどうなっちゃったんだ……？[%p]"
msgstr "21300:I'd been just fine when I got here. What had happened to me?[%p]"

msgid "21400:すごく苦しくて、[linebreak]我慢できなくなり、[%p]"
msgstr "21400:I was in so much pain. I just couldn't take it.[%p]"

msgid "21500:ナースステーションにいる看護師に、助けを求めようとした。[%p]"
msgstr "21500:I decided to get help from one of the nurses at the nurse's station.[%p]"

msgid "21600:でも、ひとりしかいなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "21600:But there was only one person there.[%p]"

msgid "21700:どうやら僕の存在に気付いてないらしく、僕に背中を向けた状態で、何事かをぶつぶつとつぶやきながら仕事に没頭している。[%p]"
msgstr "21700:Evidently, she hadn't noticed me. She had her back turned, and was muttering something as she worked.[%p]"

msgid "21800:手にしているのはクリップボード。そこに挟んだ用紙に、なにかを書き込んでいる。[%p]"
msgstr "21800:There was a clipboard in her hand. She was writing something on the paper it held.[%p]"

msgid "21900:あ……！[%p]"
msgstr "21900:Oh![%p]"

msgid "22000:この人、何度か会ったことがあるぞ。[linebreak]看護師の葉月さんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "22000:I'd met her before! It was Hazuki, the nurse.[%p]"

msgid "22100:そうか、ここはＡＨ東京総合病院の精神科。彼女がいて当然だ。僕だってこの１ヶ月だけでも２回もお世話になっている。[%p]"
msgstr "22100:That's right. This was the mental ward at AH Tokyo General Hospital. Of course she'd be here. I'd talked to her twice in just the last month.[%p]"

msgid "22200:それならちょうどいい、彼女に声をかければ、すぐに介抱してくれるはず――[%p]"
msgstr "22200:Perfect. If she saw me, she'd help me out immediately.[%p]"

msgid "22300:そのとき、突然緊迫感を与えるようなコール音が響いた。[%p]"
msgstr "22300:Just then, I heard a beeping noise. It sounded important.[%p]"

msgid "22400:葉月さんはハッとしてクリップボードを置くと、手許のスイッチかなにかを操作する。[linebreak]"
msgstr "22400:Hazuki put down her clipboard and flipped a switch in front of her.[linebreak]"

msgid "22500:すぐにコール音は途切れた。[%p]"
msgstr "22500:The beeping noise stopped.[%p]"

msgid "22600:葉月さんはハッとしてクリップボードを置くと、手許のスイッチかなにかを操作する。すぐにコール音は途切れた。"
msgstr "22600:Hazuki put down her clipboard and flipped a switch in front of her. The beeping noise stopped."

msgid "22700:どうやらナースコールの呼び出しだったらしくて、彼女は慌ただしくナースステーションを飛び出していってしまった。[%p]"
msgstr "22700:Evidently someone had hit the button to call a nurse. She quickly ran out of the nurse's station.[%p]"

msgid "22800:どうして、僕に気付いてくれないんだろう。[linebreak]すぐ後ろで、こんなに苦しんでるって言うのに。[%p]"
msgstr "22800:She seemed not to notice me. I was suffering so much, just a few feet away from her, and she didn't even see me.[%p]"

msgid "22900:立っていられない。[linebreak]目眩がひどい。[%p]"
msgstr "22900:I couldn't stand. The vertigo was incredible.[%p]"

msgid "23000:僕は仕方なく、ナースステーションの中に入り、看護師さんが戻ってくるまで待っていることにする。[%p]"
msgstr "23000:Helplessly, I went inside the nurse's station and decided to wait for her to come back.[%p]"

msgid "23100:さっき葉月さんが立っていた場所にスツールを見つけ、そこに腰掛けた。[%p]"
msgstr "23100:I found the stool she'd been sitting on and sat down on it.[%p]"

msgid "23200:[name]拓巳[line]「はあ……はあ……」[%p]"
msgstr "23200:[name]拓巳[line]Hahh... Hahh...[%p]"

msgid "23300:頭が痛い。[linebreak]一週間前の地震のときみたいだ。[%p]"
msgstr "23300:My head hurt so bad. It was like the earthquake a week ago.[%p]"

msgid "23400:でもあのときとは痛みの質が違う……ような気がする。[%p]"
msgstr "23400:But the pain was... different, somehow. Maybe.[%p]"

msgid "23500:なにか飲みたい。[linebreak]荒い呼吸を繰り返していたせいか、呼吸するだけでのどが痛む。[%p]"
msgstr "23500:I wanted something to drink. I'd been out of breath for so long that even breathing hurt.[%p]"

msgid "23600:何気なく周囲を見回す。[%p]"
msgstr "23600:I took a quick glance around me.[%p]"

msgid "23700:葉月さんが持っていたクリップボード。[linebreak]そこに描かれているものが、視界に入った。[%p]"
msgstr "23700:I saw the clipboard Hazuki had been writing on. I could see what was drawn on it.[%p]"

msgid "23800:[name]拓巳[line]「え…………？」[%p]"
msgstr "23800:[name]拓巳[line]Huh?[%p]"

msgid "23900:いつも、葉月さんは、診察中、優しい笑みを浮かべながら、このクリップボードになにかを書き込んでいた。[%p]"
msgstr "23900:Last time I'd seen her, she'd been smiling as she'd written something on it.[%p]"

msgid "24000:処方するべき薬の名前とか、体温の数値とかだと思っていた。[%p]"
msgstr "24000:I thought she was taking down my temperature, or the names of the drugs I should be given.[%p]"

msgid "24100:[name]拓巳[line]「え……？」[%p]"
msgstr "24100:[name]拓巳[line]Huh?[%p]"

msgid "24200:だから、なぜそこに、それが描かれているのか、[linebreak]僕は理解できなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "24200:So... what was this? I couldn't understand.[%p]"

msgid "24300:[name]拓巳[line]「これ……って……？」[%p]"
msgstr "24300:[name]拓巳[line]Isn't this...[%p]"

msgid "24400:以前にも、どこかで――[%p]"
msgstr "24400:I'd seen it somewhere before.[%p]"

msgid "24500:このへたくそな絵を、僕は見たことがある――[%p]"
msgstr "24500:I'd seen this terrible drawing somewhere before.[%p]"

msgid "24600:どこだった？[linebreak]どこで、これを……？[%p]"
msgstr "24600:W-Where...? Where had I seen it?[%p]"

msgid "24700:頭が痛い。[linebreak]刺すような痛み。[%p]"
msgstr "24700:My head hurt so bad. The stabbing pain...[%p]"

msgid "24800:うなじのあたりにはチリチリとした感覚。[%p]"
msgstr "24800:The prickling at the back of my neck...[%p]"

msgid "24900:――僕を見るな！[%p]"
msgstr "24900:—Don't look at me![%p]"

msgid "25000:クリップボードを手に取った。[linebreak]カルテのような用紙が何枚も挟んである。[%p]"
msgstr "25000:I picked up the clipboard. There were several papers there, all medical charts.[%p]"

msgid "25100:めくってみた。[%p]"
msgstr "25100:I flipped through them.[%p]"

msgid "25200:２枚目にも、まったく同じへたくそな絵。[%p]"
msgstr "25200:The second one had the same terrible picture.[%p]"

msgid "25300:さらにめくる。[%p]"
msgstr "25300:I flipped to the next.[%p]"

msgid "25400:３枚目も同じ。[%p]"
msgstr "25400:The third one was the same.[%p]"

msgid "25500:４枚目も。５枚目も。６枚目も。[%p]"
msgstr "25500:The fourth, too. And the fifth. And the sixth.[%p]"

msgid "25600:どれも、同じ絵が繰り返し落書きされていた。[%p]"
msgstr "25600:They all had the same picture on them.[%p]"

msgid "25700:この絵は――[%p]"
msgstr "25700:This picture...[%p]"

msgid "25800:『張り付け』だ。[%p]"
msgstr "25800:It was “Crucified.”[%p]"

msgid "25900:そして７枚目には――[%p]"
msgstr "25900:And the seventh was...[%p]"

